text:
A nice and cozy place to chill and relax for happy hour.

One jug of Tiger beer cost $27++ and bucket of 5 bottle cost $35++.

Cool place to chill. There are live band in certain day, aside from the usual table dice game, get busy from pool game, darts, singing & drinking. Huge cushion seats. Crowds vary from young to old, Every patrons here are friendly.
Friendly pub with live singing.  The people here are friendly and the vibe is fun.
Overpriced place. A can of green tea cost $10 without informing customer beforehand. Avoid if you want to get chop.
